  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Vildagliptin Compared to Placebo on the Incretin Effect in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes Treated With Metformin</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Single-center, Double-blind, Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Cross-over Study to Assess the Effect of Vildagliptin on the Incretin Effect in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes Treated With Metformin</official_title>
